data.description: New price. The home is available for immediate occupancy. Bay Counties, College Station, is a beautiful new community with Camben Home construction. This brick home, built in 2022 has a spacious floor plan, custom solid wood cabinets, Quartz counter tops, Upgraded light fixtures, doors, Insulation, Trim, Low E windows, Luxury Vinyl flooring, Stand alone tubs. Window shades stay. Washer/Dryer negotiable. No furnishings. The meticulous owners have provided many property upgrades including touch kitchen faucets, cabinet storage system, and mini blind glass patio doors. The back patio is screened in with a fenced in backyard. Small pond behind the property. Gutters installed. Property in a desirable cul de sac. No rear neighbors.  Neighborhood has under ground utilities, lighted streets.  A long side by side driveway. Zoysia Grass and landscaping! SHORT TERM RENTAL ALLOWED. Let College Station be your next move forward.... Cornell Floor Plan
